snippet.title: Hollow Knight [Grimm Troupe DLC] - A 100% Complete Guide!!!
snippet.description:
All secret bosses, all new locations, secret lore, and more! We tell you how to fight the Nightmare King, all new charm locations, and how to prepare for the Path of Pain, a new platforming challenge in the White Palace! The free Grimm Troupe DLC gives us a ton of new secrets and adventures, so let's get started!

MUSIC: Hollow Knight Official Soundtrack
